<HEADLINE> Mongolian President Makes New Year Address </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ULAN BATOR, December 31 (Xinhua) -- Mongolian President
Nachagyn Bagahandy Wednesday called on all Mongolians to work hard
for national development and improve their own living.
</P>
