9.5 percent in 1998, up from 6.6 percent this year.
</P>
<P>
For this goal, the government will continue to encourage
foreign investment in Mozambique, support domestic enterprises
and improve economic growth mechanism, he said.
</P>
<P>
He also suggested that the government will make efforts to
safeguard public order and social safety, reduce unemployment and
eliminate unequality between men and women.  
