<TEXT>
<P>
COLOMBO, January 1 (Xinhua) -- Sri Lankan President Chandrika
Kumaratunga in a new year message to the nation on Wednesday has
called for dedication of the people to build a truly independent
nation.
</P>
<P>
Recalling that this year is the country's 50th anniversary of
independence, the president said they should look back at the path
they had traversed and chart the best course forward.
</P>
